<m0>16 days that shook the Mideast (--) and boosted Peres<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 1 IS .20 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .444 INCHES<m2><ql>
